title: Work With Me
description: I'm available for hire as a technical consultant. I'm also open to research collaborations.

body.raw:
<Callout>
    I specialize in navigating the technical challenges associated with applying machine learning to real-world problems.
</Callout>


I can provide the most value to someone who has an idea of a **new product or service they want to build**, but **doesn't have the technical expertise** to do so. 

I'll work with you to understand your goals, and then help you build a prototype that can be used to test your idea.

If you just want to chat, I happy to do that too. Reach out to me!

### Contact

<Callout type='warning'>
    Find me on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/beneverman) or [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/beneverman/). You can also email me at [evermanben@gmail.com](mailto:evermanben@gmail.com).
</Callout>
